1 - Smart gloves will be most frequently utilised in quality control, dispatching and manipulation;
2 - Smart watches will be most needed in nonconformity management;
3 - RFID technology will record the biggest growth in dispatching;
4 - Barcodes a QR codes will record the growth of their utilisation mostly in logistic processes;
5 - Drones will be more frequently used in logistic processes;
6 - Autonomous vehicles will dominate in warehousing, dispatching and transportation
